/a>   <BR><img src=http://www.opeth.com/images/still_thumb.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: evade success, needs upgrade, thoughts?</span><hr size=1> Dont know why anyone would seriously complain about evade not working enough. I know I bitch about it occasionally when I fail in a fight, but hell, it still works.<br>
When they added evade, thrilled me to death, used to be the only way to lower agro was attack a little, back of, then attack once agro went back on to the tank, most of the time just end up tanking. Now I can constantly melee with Salandrite in the main hand, and primal in off hand  and with evade, I get average of 90% back in a fight, with lots of thunderstrike proc. Just know how to mantain your agro.<br>
 <p><center>
<a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=40772 ><br><b>Jarak Mase</b> (60th level Assassin)</a>
<br>
<b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=100614">Adinus Griffonheart</b> (53rd level Wanderer)
</a>
<br>
<img src="http://users.iol.it/okandrea/inny.jpg">
<br>
<br>
